location.Description: The geo-location where the resource lives

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

properties.Description: The properties used to create a new server group.

createdBy.Description: The identity that created the resource.

createdByType.Description: The type of identity that created the resource.

lastModifiedBy.Description: The identity that last modified the resource.

lastModifiedByType.Description: The type of identity that last modified the resource.

lastModifiedAt.Description: The timestamp of resource last modification (UTC)

createMode.Description: The mode to create a new server group.

administratorLogin.Description: The administrator's login name of servers in server group. Can only be specified when the server is being created (and is required for creation).

administratorLoginPassword.Description: The password of the administrator login.

backupRetentionDays.Description: The backup retention days for server group.

postgresqlVersion.Description: The PostgreSQL version of server group.

citusVersion.Description: The Citus version of server group.

enableMx.Description: If Citus MX is enabled or not for the server group.

enableZfs.Description: If ZFS compression is enabled or not for the server group.

enableShardsOnCoordinator.Description: If shards on coordinator is enabled or not for the server group.

state.Description: A state of a server group that is visible to user.

earliestRestoreTime.Description: The earliest restore point time (ISO8601 format) for server group.

resourceProviderType.Description: The resource provider type of server group.

serverRoleGroups.Description: The list of server role groups.

maintenanceWindow.Description: Maintenance window of a server group.

availabilityZone.Description: Availability Zone information of the server group.

standbyAvailabilityZone.Description: Standby Availability Zone information of the server group.

delegatedSubnetArguments.Description: The delegated subnet arguments for a server group.

privateDnsZoneArguments.Description: The private dns zone arguments for a server group.

readReplicas.Description: The array of read replica server groups.

sourceServerGroup.Description: The source server group id for read replica server groups.

sourceSubscriptionId.Description: The source subscription id to restore from. It's required when 'createMode' is 'PointInTimeRestore' or 'ReadReplica'

sourceResourceGroupName.Description: The source resource group name to restore from. It's required when 'createMode' is 'PointInTimeRestore' or 'ReadReplica'

sourceServerGroupName.Description: The source server group name to restore from. It's required when 'createMode' is 'PointInTimeRestore' or 'ReadReplica'

sourceLocation.Description: The source server group location to restore from. It's required when 'createMode' is 'PointInTimeRestore' or 'ReadReplica'

pointInTimeUTC.Description: Restore point creation time (ISO8601 format), specifying the time to restore from. It's required when 'createMode' is 'PointInTimeRestore'

serverEdition.Description: The edition of a server (default: GeneralPurpose).

storageQuotaInMb.Description: The storage of a server in MB (max: 2097152 = 2TiB).

vCores.Description: The vCores count of a server (max: 64).

enableHa.Description: If high availability is enabled or not for the server.

enablePublicIp.Description: If public IP is requested or not for a server.

name.Description: The name of the server role group.

role.Description: The role of servers in the server role group.

serverCount.Description: The number of servers in the server role group.

serverNames.Description: The list of server names in the server role group.

fullyQualifiedDomainName.Description: The fully qualified domain name of a server.

customWindow.Description: indicates whether custom window is enabled or disabled

dayOfWeek.Description: day of week for maintenance window

privateDnsZoneArmResourceId.Description: private dns zone arm resource id.

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

properties.Description: The properties of a server group firewall rule.

startIpAddress.Description: The start IP address of the server group firewall rule. Must be IPv4 format.

endIpAddress.Description: The end IP address of the server group firewall rule. Must be IPv4 format.

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

properties.Description: The properties of a server group role.

password.Description: The password of the server group role.
